<COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">The report</COREF> held that the effect that the Asian banking crisis was having on <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">the world economy</COREF> was even more serious than previously estimated .
<COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">It</COREF> <COREF ID="15" TYPE="IDENT">estimated</COREF> that for <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">the world economy</COREF> <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">this year 's</COREF> rate of growth would be 4.1 % , <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">next year</COREF> falling to 3.5 % , and that <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">this year</COREF> is the year with the slowest growth in the last 5 years .
