<COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">The IMF</COREF> furthermore lowered the forecasts of <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">next year 's</COREF> economic growth for a large number of regions and countries .
According to <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> newest estimates , the rate of economic growth of <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">industrialized countries</COREF> <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">this year</COREF> will be 3.9 % and <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">next year</COREF> it will be 3.6 % .
